1058
00:43:28.581 --> 00:43:29.723
(yelps)

1059
00:43:29.758 --> 00:43:31.725
You mean like this?

1060
00:43:31.760 --> 00:43:33.584
Yes. Mack. It's working.

1061
00:43:33.619 --> 00:43:34.794
♪ ♪

1062
00:43:34.829 --> 00:43:36.796
